644
00:48:06,500 --> 00:48:08,070
What?

645
00:48:15,570 --> 00:48:20,490
 He was Boo Yi's older brother? The Viper? 

646
00:48:22,410 --> 00:48:27,220
I can vaguely remember you after seeing your face.

647
00:48:27,220 --> 00:48:30,210
We hid together in Dohwajun.

648
00:48:31,200 --> 00:48:35,490
