00:49:25,660 --> 00:49:29,430
We are trying to make a reality

664
00:49:30,220 --> 00:49:32,990
that we've never seen in this world.

665
00:49:35,680 --> 00:49:39,270
Blood? Tears?

666
00:49:40,800 --> 00:49:49,380
Yes, that blood is the problem. Didn't I tell you? For your plans and process how much blood do you need?

667
00:49:51,030 --> 00:49:53,960
You answered in this way.

668
00:49:55,060 --> 00:49:57,710
